-09-29T07:39:30.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"9546337f5674ba3bbfdf4ead085d7a9df628c8ef","tid":1601473,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"772f7dfe2ce9cc12a944c4587f6cffac462c5250","tid":1601473,"uid":249243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:39:30.000Z","msg":"721"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:39:52.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"951783ceed1d1ca9a3aaa58037e73547811befdb","tid":1601473,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7574efd67c79d7b820d2c3fbc87ce9020745fb3f","tid":1601473,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:10:21.000Z","msg":"💩"},{"pid":"1876b551e101f411287014b82972390eb5604d1e","tid":1601473,"uid":13428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10222a4ac227d40bc9a9875246ae85b0bc46f461","tid":1601473,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:14:37.000Z","msg":"全民核彈！全部軍師立即響應美國，草擬制裁港共企業名單！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1599761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1599761</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">美國已經批准審核香港人權及民主法案2019，<span style=\"color: red;\">國會議員可以制定制裁名單。</span><br />\n請各位軍師善用呢個機會，<span style=\"color: gold;\">依家大家應搜集一切過往新聞片段、照片、新聞報導、政府新聞公告等一切資料，羅列所有協助侵犯香港人權嘅個人、企業嘅罪證</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">整理好一份名單，寄俾美國嘅國會議員</span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只要佢哋落入《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法案》嘅制裁名單，咁個人或公司經濟即刻受到重創。咁呢班商人到時就會調轉槍頭，向政府施壓要求政府讓步及妥協。</span><br />\n我在此拋磚引玉，請大家接力發掘：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察</span></strong>：非法鎮壓、濫捕和平示威者，無顯示警員編號及無出示委任證，應全體受到制裁。所以請大家依家要整理好現役警員清單。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">律政司</span></strong>：無理監控<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府新聞處</span></strong>：惡意抹黑示威者，為港共政權掩飾罪證。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黨鐵</strong></span>：多次協助警察鎮壓示威者，721車務控制中心落order迫停列車，任由黑幫恐怖襲擊。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>新雄雞</strong></span>：縱容警察在其屬下商場毆打、濫捕示威者<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">狗巴、八達通</span></strong>：將示威者八達通資料交與警察抓捕<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國國務院港澳辦、中國外交部、中聯辦、人民日報、中央電視台、環球時報、太公文匯報、賣過百份報、黨媒01、巫線、腥賭日報</span></strong>：惡意抹黑示威者，散播仇恨言論，為港共政權掩飾罪證。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>富臨</strong></span>：主動為參與鎮壓和平示威者嘅黑幫提供膳食。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>國家民航局、國泰、拮野家</strong></span>：打壓參與示威嘅員工、或以政治原因炒員工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中國政法委</strong></span>：打壓及恐嚇李嘉誠同情年輕人的言論<br />\n等等。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地要做嘅係，向美國參眾議員建議制裁名單及佢地罪證。一旦制裁名單上嘅人士、企業受到美國制裁，以後就無人及公司可以同佢做生意。否則同受制裁。</span></strong></span>例子如下：</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中國企業違反伊朗制裁令 美國務卿：將進行懲罰</strong><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">美國國務卿龐皮歐（Mike Pompeo）周三（9/25）表示，部分中國公司及個人因違反伊朗制裁禁令，而正接受美國的相關制裁。\n \n美國之音報導，美國財政部周三在其官網上公佈了這次最新制裁的對象，包括5名中國公民和6家中國實體。龐皮歐在紐約聯大會議期間參加一次會議時說：「正如我們對中國和所有國家所說的那樣：要知道我們將對每一次違反禁令進行制裁。」\n \n龐皮歐還說，華府正努力讓各國了解跟伊朗革命衛隊做生意的風險，美國將懲罰那些違反制裁並且繼續跟伊朗接觸的實體和個人。\n \n據悉，這6家被制裁的中國實體是中遠海運（大連）有限公司、大連中遠海運油運船員船舶管理有限公司、中和石油有限公司、昆侖航運有限公司，昆侖控股有限公司和飛馬88有限公司。\nhttps://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190926/1639203</code></pre>"},{"pid":"c659257db35cfa815c6d6199c5a7ce0d041a3390","tid":1601473,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef14b2790e792fe5b19d520bb9ad0accb170c62","tid":1601473,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa4a93ac967547be8d9dcdcc508a01dba89c6ce","tid":1601473,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"大埔要人"},{"pid":"66114409dc6eb53de94f84a723c3f32859f2f3f1","tid":1601473,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01571e8e8ef9445fbacc2052bf79996183b71bb","tid":1601473,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:47:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"787f743cd47d4690e4bbd50df372566fef4b1d78","tid":1601473,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e102daa9b410028fed852a1e9eb3944fc3231fc6","tid":1601473,"uid":37715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"<i